overview: Woooooo-weeeee! Here we go again with the best of the best in this special 2-disc collector's edition featuring the biggest and boldest names in the business. We've got Carmen Luvana, Cytherea, Jenna Haze, Nautica Thorn, Lacie Heart, Eva Angelina, Lela Star, Naomi, Julia Bond, Paulina James, and more. So if you can't take the heat, then get your ass out of the kitchen. These girls are on a mission, and they're fantasy all-stars!
title: Fantasy All-Stars 4
